4Geeks Academy offers a 16-week Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience, aiming to develop skills to protect digital environments. The program includes three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants, ensuring personalized attention. Students will learn about Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST will also be covered. Participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate upon finishing the course. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop